Q">Sơn hành phùng tiều giả - 山行逢樵者</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Cung/author-cDUIMuAqZhyluXUiTPluKw">Hồ Trọng Cung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Ch%C3%AD/Tha-nh%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B5-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-m%C3%A3/poem-SAbM1MXRAjdqhsEp_3gqug">Tha nhân kỵ đại mã - 他人騎大馬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Ch%C3%AD/author-NWApMYZoTzqmQhNCchcTgQ">Vương Phạm Chí</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/Th%C3%B9-ch%C6%B0-c%C3%B4ng-ki%E1%BA%BFn-qu%C3%A1/poem-Tz8vWHWQkWWRTYQ4Xaqoyw">Thù chư công kiến quá - 酬諸公見過</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-T%E1%BA%A3o/Ti%E1%BB%81u-phu/poem-k0yYtq5vRurc_48v2cUo6g">Tiều phu - 樵夫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-T%E1%BA%A3o/author-F2dFnt8mNMhC28_w-RcAWg">Tiêu Đức Tảo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%C3%B4-T%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-sfdvn31_jpZuiCvXr84e8g">Tô Tần đình kỳ 2 - 蘇秦亭其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
